d%20into%20a%20home%20wasn't%20as%20easy%20as%20I%20expected%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Small%20kitchen%20with%20yellow%20fridge%2C%20white%20cabinets%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ec5457b8b41a9673fc5a5c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEventually%2C%20we%20created%20a%20space%20with%20a%20full%20kitchen%20and%20bathroom.%20%3Cp%3ETiana%20Molony%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20April%2C%20my%20mom%20began%20meeting%20with%20contractors%20to%20plan%20out%20the%20shed-turned-home's%20layout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20tough%20to%20fit%20everything%20we%20wanted%20in%20the%20small%20space%2C%20but%20we%20settled%20on%20a%20one-bedroom%2C%20one-bathroom%20design.%20The%20living%20room%20and%20kitchen%20would%20be%20one%20space%20divided%20by%20a%20couch%2C%20and%20the%20bathroom%20would%20contain%20a%20stacked%20washer%2Fdryer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20foolishly%20thought%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finterior-design-trends-that-should-be-in-more-homes-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edesigning%20a%20house%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20be%20as%20simple%20as%20paying%20Sims%20%E2%80%94%20pick%20your%20paint%2C%20choose%20your%20floor%2C%20and%2C%20boom%2C%20all%20done.%20As%20it%20turns%20out%2C%20it's%20a%20lot%20more%20complicated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Small%20sofa%20chair%20with%20side%20table%2C%20lamp%2C%20and%20wall%20art%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ec53abb8b41a9673fc5a25%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20living-room%20space%20is%20fairly%20open.%20%3Cp%3ETiana%20Molony%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20process%2C%20we%20experienced%20numerous%20setbacks%2C%20like%20getting%20plumbers%2C%20electricians%2C%20and%20contractors%20to%20even%20show%20up.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20them%20had%20prior%20commitments%20and%20were%20working%20on%20our%20tiny%20home%20as%20a%20side%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bed%20in%20white%20room%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ec53ab69253ccddf9af3f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20bedroom%20even%20has%20a%20window.%20%3Cp%3ETiana%20Molony%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20us%20about%20a%20month%20to%20find%20a%20plumber%2C%20then%20we%20ended%20up%20having%20to%20dig%20a%20tunnel%20below%20the%20shed%20to%20connect%20our%20lines%20directly%20to%20the%20plumbing%20in%20the%20main%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20struggled%20to%20connect%20an%20Ethernet%20to%20the%20tiny%20home.%20My%20dad%20had%20to%20run%20conduit%20from%20the%20main%20house%20underground%20and%20funnel%20Ethernet%20through%20it.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20in%20all%2C%20the%20project%20took%20about%20five%20months%20to%20complete.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2260bf071b-d543-4ae6-a3df-083602310dfc%5C%22%3EWe're%20grateful%20to%20live%20somewhere%20we%20can%20have%20our%20own%20space%20and%20also%20save%20money%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tiny%20home%2C%20converted%20shed%2C%20with%20steps%20and%20deck%20area%20leading%20up%20to%20it%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ec54a0b8b41a9673fc5a6b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20tiny%20home%20allows%20us%20to%20save%20money%20for%20the%20home%20we%20hope%20to%20buy%20someday.%20%3Cp%3ETiana%20Molony%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20we%20finally%20moved%20into%20the%20converted%20storage%20shed%20on%20the%20northwestern%20corner%20of%20my%20parents'%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20grateful%20my%20parents%20funded%20this%20project%20and%20don't%20charge%20us%20rent.%20We%20have%20regular%20monthly%20expenses%2C%20like%20groceries%20and%20gas%2C%20but%20we're%20able%20to%20save%20most%20of%20our%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20not%20having%20to%20pay%20rent%20has%20helped%20me%20sustain%20my%20career%20as%20a%20freelance%20writer.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recognize%20how%20fortunate%20we%20are%20to%20be%20in%20this%20position.%20Still%2C%20my%20partner%20and%20I%20don't%20plan%20to%20live%20here%20forever.%20My%20parents%20built%20this%20space%20with%20the%20idea%20that%20when%20we%20move%20out%2C%20they%20can%20use%20it%20accommodate%20guests%20or%20other%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20it's%20our%20home%2C%20allowing%20us%20to%20live%20where%20we%20want%20without%20spending%20most%20of%20our%20income%20on%20rent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20incredibly%20lucky%20to%20get%20to%20spend%20our%20days%20surrounded%20by%20nature%20in%20the%20town%20where%20we%20grew%20up%2C%20cozily%20nestled%20between%20the%20mountains%20and%20the%20sea.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-built-tiny-home-for-me-on-property-rent-free-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744373042000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ec53abb8b41a9673fc5a24%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-built-tiny-home-for-me-on-property-rent-free-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20parents%20built%20a%20tiny%20home%20on%20their%20property%20in%20Santa%20Barbara%2C%20California%2C%20out%20of%20a%20shed.%20I%20live%20there%20rent-free%20while%20saving%20to%20buy%20a%20house.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Tiana%20Molony%20)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A110%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-built-tiny-home-for-me-on-property-rent-