2C%20our%20opinions%20are%20our%20own.%20See%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fpersonal-finance-editorial-standards%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20we%20rate%20products%20and%20services%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20you%20make%20smart%20decisions%20with%20your%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20a%20man%20wearing%20a%20business%20suit%20and%20a%20woman%20wearing%20a%20running%20outfit.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e7135eb8b41a9673fc14c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEric%20Roberge%20and%20Karina%20Ripps.%3Cp%3EBeyond%20Your%20Hammock%2C%20Rachel%20Lehman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI'm%20a%20financial%20planner%2C%20and%20I%20helped%20one%20of%20my%20clients%20start%20a%20personal%20training%20business.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20would%20normally%20never%20advise%20cutting%20retirement%20savings%2C%20but%20that%20was%20key%20to%20going%20all%20in%20on%20her%20business.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHaving%20a%20financial%20planner%20who%20can%20assess%20your%20business%20plan%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20find%20clarity.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fcfp%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancial%20planner%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20things%20to%20do%20within%20the%20wealth%20management%20firm%20I%20started%2012%20years%20ago%20is%20helping%20other%20aspiring%20entrepreneurs%20reach%20their%20own%20goals%20of%20launching%20successful%20ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20exactly%20what%20we%20got%20to%20do%20last%20year%20with%20one%20of%20our%20amazing%20clients%2C%20Karina%20Ripps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERipps%20is%20a%20certified%20run%20coach%2C%20a%20personal%20trainer%2C%20a%20nutritionist%2C%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.karinaripps.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERipps%20on%20the%20Run%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20and%20her%20team%20of%20coaches%20help%20runners%20hit%20their%20long-term%20goals%20through%20coaching%20and%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20being%20the%20CEO%20of%20her%20company%20is%20Ripps'%20full-time%20job.%20But%20when%20we%20started%20working%20together%2C%20she%20still%20worked%20a%20corporate%20job%20%E2%80%94%20and%20she%20was%20determined%20to%20start%20devoting%20all%20her%20time%20and%20energy%20to%20her%20own%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229849fb4e-6ff1-4be0-8a02-cf7d9d9a433c%5C%22%3EMaking%20the%20transition%20from%20successful%20side%20hustle%20to%20full-time%20entrepreneurship%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERipps%20started%20Ripps%20on%20the%20Run%20in%20the%20depths%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20while%20juggling%20a%20full-time%20corporate%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20late%202020%2C%20she%20made%20a%20bold%20move%20%E2%80%94%20investing%20%241%2C500%20in%20a%20business%20coach.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20no%20income%20from%20my%20business%2C%20and%20I%20remember%20texting%20a%20friend%2C%20panicking%2C%26quot%3B%20Ripps%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20bet%20on%20herself%20paid%20off%3A%20She%20made%20%2450%2C000%20in%20her%20first%2012%20months%20after%20launching%20her%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20more%20from%20this%20series%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flessons-entrepreneurs-founder-coffee-shop-chain-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20coffee%20shop%20founder's%20blueprint%20for%20small-business%20success%20has%206%20key%20rules%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20stayed%20on%20that%20grind%20for%20three%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Ripps%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bjuggling%20my%20full-time%20job%2C%20marathon%20training%2C%20and%20my%20growing%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERipps%20and%20I%20worked%20together%20to%20confirm%20that%20her%20goal%20to%20quit%20her%209-to-5%20and%20focus%20on%20building%20the%20business%20wasn't%20just%20a%20leap%20of%20faith.%20It%20was%20a%20strategic%2C%20financially%20sound%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20focused%20on%20three%20areas%20of%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Ffinancial-plan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancial%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20she%20could%20confidently%20move%20into%20the%20role%20of%20full-time%20entrepreneur%20and%20business%20owner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22081aa5e3-d629-40c2-a93e-a6525b04a9a9%5C%22%3E1.%20Controlling%20(and%20freeing%20up)%20cash%20flow%20by%20reducing%20retirement%20savings%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERipps'%20business%20was%20generating%20a%20healthy%20amount%20of%20income%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20yet%20replace%20her%20full-time%20salary%20(and%20in%20Boston%2C%20where%20we%20both%20are%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20is%20sky-high).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnowing%20this%2C%20her%20biggest%20priority%20would%20be%20to%20reduce%20money%20going%20out%20the%20door.%20The%20less%20she%20%3Cem%3Ehad%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20spend%2C%20the%20more%20she%20reduced%20the%20chances%20she'd%20need%20to%20dip%20too%20far%20into%20savings%20and%20the%20more%20runway%20she%20could%20create%20for%20her%20business%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20advised%20Ripps%20to%20not%20just%20minimize%20extra%20spending%20in%20the%20short%20term%2C%20but%20also%20stop%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fbest-retirement-plans%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaving%20for%20retirement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20goes%20counter%20to%20almost%20any%20financial%20advice%20out%20there%2C%20but%20there%20are%20situations%20in%20which%20it%20makes%20more%20sense%20to%20invest%20in%20yourself%20now%20than%20in%20your%20very%20long-term%20financial%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERipps%20found%20that%20reassurance%20was%20invaluable.%20%26quot%3BI%20gave%20my%20business%20100%25%2C%20and%20that%20made%20all%20the%20difference%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c84a996f-7fef-4157-922c-2bd3bea6b8d0%5C%22%3E2.%20Developing%20structure%20and%20clarity%20with%20ongoing%20support%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERipps%20never%20lacked%20grit%2C%20determination%2C%20or%20initiative%3B%20launching%20a%20run%20coaching%20gig%20during%20the%20pandemic%20already%20proved%20she%20had%20the%20business%20acumen%20and%20drive%20to%20succeed%20without%20relying%20on%20a%20full-time%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20you%20have%20so%20much%20going%20on%2C%20it%20can%20be%20hard%20to%20step%20back%20from%20a%20massive%20goal%20and%20see%20a%20clear%2C%20organized%20order%20of%20operations%20to%20take%20you%20from%20here%20to%20where%20you%20want%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20so%20deep%20in%20the%20daily%20grind%20between%20coaching%2C%20working%20my%209-to-5%2C%20training%2C%20and%20handling%20life%20that%20I%20didn't%20have%20the%20mental%20bandwidth%20to%20sit%20down%20and%20make%20sense%20of%20my%20finances%2C%26quot%3B%20Ripps%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BHaving%20a%20second%20set%20of%20eyes%20on%20my%20numbers%20was%20invaluable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20first%20sat%20down%20to%20create%20a%20financial%20plan%20together%2C%20based%20on%20assumptions%20around%20personal%20expenses%20and%20expected%20business%20revenue%20growth%20over%20time%2C%20we%20decided%20that%20quitting%20her%20corporate%20job%20to%20focus%20on%20her%20business%20was%20a%20reasonable%20move%20to%20make.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c0943429-b6e5-4d59-abcd-9ed59cf4e434%5C%22%3E3.%20Creating%20contingency%20plans%2C%20just%20in%20case%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20a%20strong%20plan%2C%20no%20transition%20is%20risk-free.%20To%20protect%20her%20financial%20stability%2C%20we%20outlined%20a%20clear%20backup%20plan%3A%20If%20business%20growth%20was%20sl