tariff-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20was%20already%20nearly%20impossible%20to%20buy%20a%20BYD%20in%20the%20US%2C%20but%20the%20global%20trade%20war%20between%20Trump%20and%20China%20has%20made%20it%20even%20harder.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tcarter%40businessinsider.com%20(Tom%20Carter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A357%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-electric-car-get-ready-to-pay-250-percent-tariff-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Maharashtra%3A%20Is%20The%20'Marathi%20Manoos'%20Still%20Listening%20To%20Raj%20Thackeray%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20late%20Bal%20Thackeray's%20Marathi%20card%20that%20had%20once%20propelled%20Shiv%20Sena%20to%20the%20top%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20India's%20financial%20capital.%C2%A0Now%2C%20with%20a%20string%20of%20electoral%20defeats%20behind%20him%2C%20Raj%20Thackeray%2C%20the%20flamboyant%20nephew%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20founder%2C%20is%20seeking%20to%20take%20a%20leaf%20out%20of%20his%20uncle's%20book.%20The%20Maharashtra%20Navnirman%20Sena%20(MNS)%20chief%20is%20trying%20to%20re-establish%20relevance%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20other%20urban%20centres%20ahead%20of%20the%20upcoming%20municipal%20elections%20by%20reviving%20the%20'Marathi%20manoos'%20plank%20through%20the%20Marathi%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20ago%2C%20a%20combative%20Thackeray%20stirred%20controversy%20by%20warning%20that%20his%20party%20would%20not%20hesitate%20to%20%26quot%3Bslap%26quot%3B%20those%20who%20refuse%20to%20speak%20Marathi%20in%20the%20state.%20His%20aim%20is%20clear%3A%20to%20encroach%20upon%20the%20'son%20of%20the%20soil'%20space%20traditionally%20held%20by%20the%20Shiv%20Sena.%20The%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20faction%20is%20still%20reeling%20from%20its%20assembly%20election%20setback%2C%20while%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Sena%20is%20struggling%20to%20assert%20itself%20amid%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party's%20(BJP)%20growing%20dominance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Now-Or-Never%20Battle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimultaneously%2C%20Raj%20Thackeray%20is%20signalling%20a%20willingness%20to%20align%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20consolidated%20its%20position%20in%20Maharashtra%20a%20decade%20after%20emerging%20as%20the%20state's%20largest%20party.%20For%20Raj%2C%20the%20municipal%20polls%20represent%20a%20now-or-never%20opportunity%20to%20revive%20his%20political%20fortunes.%20His%20party%20failed%20to%20win%20a%20single%20assembly%20seat%2C%20and%20even%20his%20son%20Amit%20lost%20in%20their%20family%20stronghold.%20Though%20known%20for%20his%20oratory%20and%20style%20reminiscent%20of%20his%20uncle%2C%20Raj%20Thackeray%20has%20never%20contested%20an%20election%20himself.%20His%20current%20campaign%20seems%20aimed%20not%20just%20at%20voters%2C%20but%20at%20the%20BJP-to%20remind%20it%20that%20he%20still%20holds%20sway%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20BJP%2C%20these%20elections%20are%20a%20chance%20to%20further%20marginalise%20Uddhav's%20party%20while%20preventing%20Shinde%20from%20gaining%20too%20much%20ground.%20Balancing%20these%20interests%20requires%20deft%20political%20management.%20Interestingly%2C%20Shinde's%20Sena%20has%20not%20championed%20the%20'Marathi%20Manoos'%20cause%2C%20and%20is%20often%20seen%20as%20the%20BJP's%20'B%20team'.%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%2C%20often%20dubbed%20the%20'C%20team'%2C%20prioritises%20power%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20development%2C%20largely%20ignoring%20regional%20identity%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20language%20issue%20has%20regained%20emotional%20traction%20in%20a%20Mumbai%20that%20is%20increasingly%20cosmopolitan%20but%20still%20home%20to%20a%20significant%20Marathi-speaking%20population.%20No%20political%20party%20in%20Maharashtra%20can%20afford%20to%20ignore%20the%20Marathi%20language%20debate%20-%20it%20can%20either%20stir%20passions%20or%20be%20used%20to%20discredit%20opponents.%20Shiv%20Sena%20once%20led%20vigorous%20campaigns%2C%20even%20tearing%20down%20non-Marathi%20signboards.%20Those%20were%20the%20days%20when%20Bal%20Thackeray%20ruled%20Mumbai%20with%20an%20iron%20grip.%20He%20famously%20claimed%20he%20could%20shut%20down%20the%20city%20with%20just%20two%20phone%20calls%20-%20to%20PTI%20and%20UNI.%20He%20openly%20espoused%20%26quot%3Bthokshahi%26quot%3B%2C%20that%20is%2C%20rule%20by%20force%2C%20with%20his%20followers%20even%20backing%20him%20with%20action%20-%20which%20included%20vandalising%20a%20cricket%20pitch%20ahead%20of%20a%20match%20with%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20The%20Uncle%20Save%20The%20Nephew%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Raj%20Thackeray%20didn't%20split%20the%20Sena%20like%20Shinde%20did%2C%20he's%20now%20attempting%20to%20hijack%20Bal%20Thackeray's%20legacy%20through%20the%20Marathi%20plank.%20This%20comes%20as%20Uddhav's%20party%20faces%20defections%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20the%20Konkan%20region%2C%20its%20traditional%20strongholds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThackeray%20and%20the%20BJP%20may%20have%20a%20shared%20goal%20of%20limiting%20Shinde's%20influence%2C%20but%20that's%20easier%20said%20than%20done.%20Thackeray's%20biggest%20challenge%20has%20been%20his%20inconsistency.%20He%20has%20often%20been%20accused%20of%20abandoning%20causes%20midway%2C%20which%20has%20hurt%20his%20credibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20Thackeray%20has%20changed%20after%20his%20latest%20electoral%20setback%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%20He%20remains%20a%20powerful%20Marathi%20orator%2C%20reminiscent%20of%20Bal%20Thackeray%20at%20his%20peak.%20His%20success%20in%20reviving%20his%20political%20magic%20will%20be%20determined%20by%20how%20far%20the%20Marathi%20card%20takes%20him.%C2%A0Just%20yesterday%2C%20Thackeray%20issued%20a%20stern%20warning%20to%20the%20Indian%20Banks%20Association%2C%20urging%20immediate%20compliance%20with%20the%20RBI%20directive%20to%20include%20Marathi%20in%20banking%20services.%20Failure%20to%20do%20so%2C%20he%20cautioned%2C%20would%20lead%20to%20intensified%20protests%2C%20with%20banks%20bearing%20responsibility%20for%20any%20resulting%20law-and-order%20disruptions.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMarathi%20Card%20Isn't%20Going%20Anywhere%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20is%20certain%3A%20other%20parties%20will%20be%20forced%20to%20pay%20at%20least%20lip%20service%20to%20Marathi%20to%20neutralise%20Thackeray's%20appeal.%20Just%20last%20month%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20had%20to%20contain%20a%20backlash%20after%20a%20stray%20comment%20by%20a%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20leader%20in%20Mumbai%20drew%20opposition%20criticism%20over%20Marathi's%20marginalisation.%20In%20response%2C%20Fadnavis%20reaffirmed%20in%20the%20Assembly%20that%20it%20was%20not%20wrong%20to%20demand%20the%20use%20of%20Marathi%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20that%20it's%20the%20state's%20official%20language%20and%20that%20all%20residents%20must%20learn%20and%20respect%20it.%C2%A0%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20if%20someone%20takes%20the%20law%20into%20their%20hands%2C%20then%20the%20law%20will%20take%20its%20course%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%C2%A0Union%20Minister%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20expressed%20strong%20disapproval%20of%20efforts%20to%20stir%20controversy%20over%20the%20Marathi%20language%20issue%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20stating%20that%20such%20matters%20are%20usually%20short-lived%20and%20do%20not%20stay%20in%20public%20discourse%20for%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarathi%2C%20with%20over%2083%20million%20speakers%20as%20of%202011%2C%20is%20the%20third%20most%20spoken%20native%20language%20in%20India%20after%20Hindustani%20and%20Bengali.%20The%20lesson%20from%20the%20latest%20episode%20is%20that%20the%20Marathi%20card%20cannot%20and%20will%20not%20be%20ignored%2C%20even%20if%20the%20politics%20around%20it%20goes%20silent%20every%20once%20in%20a%20while.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5