sed%20in%20the%202008%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks%2C%20was%20extradited%20from%20the%20United%20States%20and%20brought%20back%20to%20India%20on%20Thursday%20evening.%20Upon%20arrival%2C%20Rana%20was%20taken%20for%20routine%20medical%20check-up%20and%20then%20produced%20before%20Special%20NIA%20Judge%20Chander%20Jit%20Singh%20for%20custody%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20was%20represented%20by%20senior%20advocate%20Dayan%20Krishnan%20and%20special%20public%20prosecutor%20Narender%20Mann.%20Rana%20was%20represented%20by%20lawyer%20Piyush%20Sachdeva%20from%20the%20Delhi%20Legal%20Services%20Authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Dayan%20Krishnan%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcanfoundation.in%2Fprofile%2Fmr-dhyan-krishnan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDayan%20Krishnan%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20Senior%20Advocate%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20a%20graduate%20of%20the%20first%20batch%20(1993)%20of%20India's%20first%20national%20law%20school%2C%20National%20Law%20School%20of%20India%20University%20(NLSIU)%2C%20Bangalore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20graduating%20in%201993%2C%20he%20worked%20with%20Senior%20Advocate%20Santosh%20Hegde%2C%20who%20later%20became%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20and%20Solicitor%20General%20of%20India.%20He%20continued%20working%20with%20Mr%20Hegde%20until%201999%2C%20after%20which%20he%20set%20up%20his%20own%20legal%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20worked%20on%20several%20high-profile%20legal%20matters%2C%20including%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%202001%20Parliament%20attack%20case%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Kaveri%20river%20water%20dispute%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EVarious%20telecommunication%20cases%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWorked%20with%20the%201999%20Justice%20JS%20Verma%20Commission%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20the%20Special%20Public%20Prosecutor%20in%20the%20December%202012%20Delhi%20gang-rape%20and%20murder%20case%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20widely%20followed%20criminal%20trials%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Krishnan%20has%20represented%20several%20key%20government%20bodies%20such%20as%20the%20Union%20of%20India%2C%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%2C%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%2C%20Delhi%20Government%2C%20and%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20in%20various%20important%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20held%20distinguished%20roles%20including%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECBI%20Special%20Prosecutor%20in%20one%20of%20the%20Commonwealth%20Games%20(CWG)%20graft%20cases%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECBI%20Special%20Prosecutor%20in%20the%20Navy%20War%20Room%20leak%20case.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECBI%20Prosecutor%20in%20the%20Delhi%20Development%20Authority%20(DDA)%20scam.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESpecial%20Prosecutor%20in%20the%20Nitish%20Katara%20murder%20case.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECounsel%20for%20Serious%20Fraud%20Investigation%20Office%20(SFIO)%20in%20the%20Satyam%20Computers%20scam.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnalsar.ac.in%2Fextradition-litigation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDayan%20Krishnan%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20appointed%20as%20Special%20Counsel%20for%20the%20NIA%20and%20was%20part%20of%20a%20team%20that%20went%20to%20Chicago%20to%20question%20David%20Coleman%20Headley%2C%20one%20of%20the%20accused%20in%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20attacks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202011%2C%20he%20represented%20the%20government%C2%A0in%20the%20extradition%20case%20of%20Ravi%20Shankaran%20from%20the%20UK.%20In%202012%2C%20he%20appeared%20as%20Special%20Counsel%20for%20the%20CBI%20in%20the%20extradition%20case%20of%20Raymond%20Varley%2C%20linked%20to%20a%20child%20sex%20abuse%20case%20in%20Goa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20he%20was%20appointed%20Special%20Public%20Prosecutor%20in%20the%20extradition%20case%20of%20David%20Headley%20and%20Tahawwur%20Rana.%20That%20same%20year%2C%20he%20was%20designated%20as%20a%20Senior%20Advocate%20by%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%2C%20becoming%20the%20second%20NLSIU%20Bangalore%20graduate%20to%20receive%20the%20honour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Narendra%20Mann%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-is-narender-mann-advocate-appointed-to-lead-prosecution-in-26-11-accused-tahawwur-rana-039-s-trial-8131134%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Mann%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20legal%20professional%20who%20has%20represented%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20in%20several%20high-profile%20cases.%20As%20per%20reports%2C%20one%20of%20the%20notable%20cases%20he%20handled%20was%20the%202018%20Staff%20Selection%20Commission%20(SSC)%20paper%20leak%20scandal.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744367580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fv7rm5koo_tahawwur-rana-_625x300_11_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmeet-the-lawyers-representing-anti-terror-agency-nia-in-tahawwur-rana-case-8139678%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tahawwur%20Rana%2C%20a%20key%20accused%20in%20the%202008%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks%2C%20was%20extradited%20from%20the%20United%20States%20and%20brought%20back%20to%20India%20on%20Thursday%20evening.%20Upon%20arrival%2C%20Rana%20was%20taken%20for%20routine%20medical%20check-up.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmeet-the-lawyers-representing-anti-terror-agency-nia-in-tahawwur-rana-case-8139678%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Zerodha%20CEO%20Nithin%20Kamath%20to%20investors%3A%20Over%20the%20next%2010%20days%2C%20there%20are%20only%20...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744367472000%2C%22visual%22