0Indian%20nationals%20from%20Myanmar%2C%20victims%20of%20forced%20cyber%20slavery%20under%20false%20job%20promises.%20Maharashtra%20Police%20arrested%20five%20agents%2C%20including%20a%20foreign%20national%2C%20involved%20in%20trafficking%20victims%20from%20Thailand%20to%20Myanmar.%20The%20victims%20were%20coerced%20into%20carrying%20out%20digital%20arrest%20and%20investment%20scams%20in%20guarded%20compounds%20controlled%20by%20armed%20groups.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fforced-to-conduct-digital-arrests-60-indians-rescued-from-myanmar-5-agents-held%2Farticleshow%2F120203048.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%2C%20EU%20trade%20talks%20moving%20forward%20with%20'India%20first'%20approach%3A%20Piyush%20Goyal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744366187000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-us-eu-trade-talks-goyal-india-first-tariff-pressure-ftas-125041100716_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20Trump's%20tariff%20threats%20looming%20across%20the%20world%2C%20Goyal%20further%20stated%20that%20India%20does%20not%20negotiate%20under%20pressure%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-us-eu-trade-talks-goyal-india-first-tariff-pressure-ftas-125041100716_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20As%20Tahawwur%20Rana%20Talks%2C%20Pakistan%20Had%20Better%20Lend%20An%20Ear%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOne%20can%20hardly%20say%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20eagle%20has%20landed%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20manner%20of%20spy%20thrillers.%20Intel%20coding%20for%20movement%20to%20India%20of%20a%20despised%20terrorist%20would%20be%20more%20like%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20carrion%20crow%20has%20been%20shackled%26quot%3B.%20For%2C%20Tahawwur%20Rana%20was%20not%20even%20a%20terrorist%20who%20risked%20his%20life%20to%20commit%20violence.%20He%20stayed%20in%20the%20shadows%2C%20pushing%20and%20guiding%20others%2C%20from%20his%20comfortable%20home%20in%20Chicago.%20But%20make%20no%20mistake.%20He's%20critical%20for%20a%20clear%20understanding%20of%20what%20happened%20not%20just%20before%20the%20Mumbai%20attacks%2C%20but%20after%20it.%20He%20was%2C%20after%20all%2C%20arrested%20only%20a%20year%20later%2C%20and%20he%20and%20David%20Headley%20began%20to%20operate%20together%20in%201997.%20That's%20nearly%2012%20years%20of%20information.%20The%20Intel%20guys%20are%20going%20to%20have%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet's%20take%20Tahawwur%20Rana%20apart%20-%20apart%20from%20the%20usual%20banalities.%20That%20he%20was%20from%20an%20elite%20family%2C%20and%20was%20able%20to%20study%20in%20the%20Pakistan%20army's%20Hassan%20Abdal%20cadet%20college%20is%20clear.%20He%20also%20went%20for%20trips%20with%20fellow%20student%20Daud%20Gilani%2C%20or%20David%20Headley%2C%20to%20the%20tribal%20areas%2C%20where%20the%20latter%20at%20least%20was%20involved%20in%20moving%20drugs%2C%20besides%20being%20a%20heroin%20addict%20himself.%20But%20Rana's%20military%20ID%20proved%20useful.%20In%201997%2C%20Rana%20migrated%20to%20Canada%2C%20but%20Headley's%20statement%20that%20he%20was%20a%20deserter%20seemed%20to%20be%20taken%20for%20granted.%20It%20is%20highly%20unlikely%20that%20the%20ISI%20would%20trust%20a%20deserter%20with%20details%20of%20one%20of%20the%20most%20sensational%20attacks%20in%20terrorism%20history.%20In%20terms%20of%20facts%2C%20what%20we%20do%20know%20from%20court%20documents%20is%20that%20he%20set%20up%20an%20Immigration%20Agency%20in%20Chicago%20and%20was%20conniving%20with%20Headley%20even%20after%20he%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Drug%20Enforcement%20Agency%2C%20and%20then%20made%20their%20'source'%2C%20which%20he%20was%20well%20aware%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeadley%20notes%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20told%20Dr%20Rana%20the%20entire%20plan%20of%20the%20LeT%20and%20lSI%2C%20and%20he%20readily%20agreed%20to%20provide%20(help).%26quot%3B%20Rana%20then%20arranged%20for%20all%20documentation%20for%20Headley%20to%20travel%20to%20India%2C%20and%20set%20up%20an%20Immigration%20'office'%20using%20falsified%20documents%2C%20even%20securing%20a%20five-year%20visa.%20All%20that%20is%20punishable%20under%20Indian%20law.%20But%2C%20more%20importantly%2C%20when%20Headley%20told%20him%20about%20the%20Lashkar-e-Taiba's%20plans%20for%20the%20Mumbai%20attack%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20smiled%20and%20laughed%26quot%3B.%20Well%2C%20he's%20not%20laughing%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERana%20As%20Confidant%20And%20Enabler%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorse%20was%20to%20follow.%20Just%20a%20month%20before%20the%20Mumbai%20attacks%2C%20Headley%20was%20approached%20by%20a%20person%20who%20still%20remains%20mysterious.%20This%20was%20a%20Sajid%20Mir%2C%20certainly%20part%20of%20the%20ISI%20inner%20circle%20of%20agents%2C%20and%20who%20was%20far%20more%20operationally%20secretive%20than%20the%20others.%20He%20was%20a%20critical%20link%20in%20getting%20Headley%20to%20plan%20an%20attack%20in%20Denmark%20against%20the%3Cem%3E%20Jyllands-Posten%3C%2Fem%3E%20newspaper%2C%20which%20had%20published%20a%20series%20of%20cartoons%20on%20the%20Prophet%20that%20led%20to%20huge%20protests%20in%20Pakistan.%20In%20that%20attack%2C%20the%20plans%20were%20gory%20in%20the%20extreme.%20The%20idea%20was%20to%20chop%20the%20targets'%20heads%20off%20and%20throw%20them%20in%20the%20street.%20Clearly%2C%20violence%20came%20very%20easily%20to%20Rana.%20Throughout%20the%20five%20or%20more%20visits%20of%20Headley%20to%20India%2C%20and%20his%20'unofficial'%20visits%20to%20meet%20his%20new%20wife%20in%20Dubai%2C%20Rana%20remained%20in%20the%20picture.%20Headley%20did%20not%20choose%20to%20tell%20his%20handlers%20about%20any%20of%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20therefore%2C%20Rana%20was%20extremely%20close%20to%20Headley.%20Presumably%2C%20he%20also%20told%20him%20about%20his%20various%20reconnaissance%20plans%2C%20including%20of%20the%20National%20Defence%20College%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20Bhawan%2C%20and%20the%20Pune%20army%20installations%20that%20Headley%20says%20he%20has%20%26quot%3Bforgotten%26quot%3B%20about.%20And%20then%2C%20the%20most%20interesting%20of%20all%3A%20about%20a%20week%20before%20the%20Mumbai%20attack%2C%20Rana%20arrived%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20travelling%20also%20to%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Kochi%2C%20Agra%2C%20Hapur%20with%20his%20wife.%20One%20now%20expects%20that%20he%20will%20be%20taken%20to%20all%20these%20places%20and%20questioned%20closely%20not%20just%20about%20who%20he%20met%2C%20but%20also%20about%20whom%20he%20spoke%20to%2C%20and%20who%20facilitated%20him.%20All%20that%20is%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGetting%20Convictions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20to%20his%20extradition%20and%20what%20he%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20convicted%20for.%20Rana%20was%20arrested%20in%202009%2C%20nearly%20seven%20years%20after%20he%20first%20began%20his%20association%20with%20Headley%20and%20Lashkar.%20Headley%20was%20arrested%20earlier%20on%20his%20way%20to%20Pakistan%2C%20together%20with%20some%2013%20surveillance%20videos%20at%20Chicago%20airport%20in%202009.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20while%20it%20seems%20the%20preparation%20for%20the%20Mumbai%20attack%20that%20was%20going%20on%20for%20years%20remained%20unknown%2C%20the%20short%20span%20of%20planning%20for%20Denmark%20was%20found%20out.%20Rana%20was%20sentenced%20to%20168%20months%2C%20which%20were%20further%20reduced%20after%20a%20plea.%20It%20was%20somewhere%20during%20this%20time%20that%20India%20asked%20for%20extradition%2C%20and%2C%20in%202020%2C%20a%20California%20judge%20finally%20issued%20a%20provisional%20warrant%20for%20this.%20Further%20rounds%20of%20pleas%20citing%20%26quot%3Bdouble%20jeopardy%26quot%3B%20were%20rejected%20by%20court%20after%20court%2C%20and%20for%20five%20years%2C%20Rana%20did%20every%20possible%20thing%20to%20avoid%20extradition%2C%20citing%20danger%20to%20himself%2C%20illness%2C%20etc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20important%20thing%20to%20note%20throughout%20this%20is%20that%20while%20his%20connection%20with%20the%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20and%20others%20in%20Pakistan%20-%20including%20one%20'Major%20Iqbal'%20-%20has%20been%20cited%20by%20Headley%2C%20he%20himself%20seems%20to%20have%20kept%20silent%20on%20his%20ISI%20connections%20throughout%20the%20trial%20period.%20That%20means%20he's%20tough%20as%20nails.%20Unless%20India%20has%20its%20own%2C%20or%20access%20to%20intercepts%20showing%20his%20specific%20involvement%20with%20the%20terrorist%20act%20itself%2C%20the%20charges%20of%20assistance%20to%20terrorists%20are%20going%20to%20be%20difficult%20to%20prove.%20There%20is%2C%20however%2C%20one%20bright%20spot.%20The%20whole%20investigation%20involves%20not%20just%20India%20but%20also%20all%20those%20countries%20whose%20nationals%20were%20killed%20or%20injured%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20attack.%20That%20includes%20Britain%2C%20Israel%20and%20Australia%2C%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20Americans%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20were%20deliberately%20picked%20out%20by%20terrorists%20on%20the%20instructions%20of%20Sajid%20Mir.%20These%20states%20have%20expressed%20their%20support%20for%20India%2C%20and%20it%20can%20be%20expected%20that%20there%20will%20be%20considerable%20intelligence-sharing%20to%20secure%20the%20conviction%20of%20Rana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20final%20analysis%2C%20this%20is%20about%20incredibly%20intricate%20planning%20by%20Pakistan.%20Remember%2C%20Headley%20himself%20was%20never%20implicated%20in%20any%20buying%20of%20explosives%2C%20weapons%2C%20or%20in%20any%20violent%20activity.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20Pakistanis%20evaded%20interception%20by%20%26quot%3Boutsourcing%26quot%3B%20critical%20enabling%20activity%20to%20foreign%20passport%20holders%2C%20and%20then%20left%20the%20actual%20killing%20to%20an%20entirely%20different%20bunch%20of%20illiterate%20goons.%20Even%20more%20notably%2C%20almost%20the%20entire%20lot%2C%20including%20Headley%2C%20Rana%20and%20persons%20like%20Abdur%20Rehman%2C%20were%20all%20formerly%20with%20the%20Pakistan%20army.%20Rehman%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20was%20from%20the%20Pakistan%20Military%20Academy%2C%20while%20the%20other%20two%20were%20from%20the%20elite%20Hassan%20Abdal%20Cadet%20school.%20Ilyas%20Kashmiri%2C%20a%20key%20member%20of%20the%20group%20also%20involved%20in%20the%20Danish%20attack%20plans%2C%20was%20possibly%20from%20the%20ultra-elite%20Special%20Services%20Group%20(SSG).%20All%20this%20is%20apart%20from%20the%20regularly%20serving%20ISI%20officers%2C%20including%20one%20Brigadier.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20it's%20only%20likely%20that%20the%20jihadi-army%20complex%20is%20deeply%20interlinked.%20Even%20with%20the%20best%20of%20intentions%20-%20and%20this%20is%20rare%20on%20the%20ground%20-%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20difficult%20to%20separate%20these.%20And%20this%20constitutes%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20the%20greatest%20threat%20to%20the%20present%20Army%20Chief%2C%20Gen.%20Asim%20Munir.%20It%20was%20this%20group%20that%20had%20plans%20to%20assassinate%20General%20Musharraf%2C%20though%20they%20were%20quashed%20by%20the%20annoyed%20Lashkar%20chief%20Zaki%20ur%20Rehman%20Lakhvi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20sum%2C%20Pakistan%20should%20be%20the%20most%20interested%20in%20the%20details%20that%20Tahawwur%20Rana%20will%20reveal.%20It%20just%20might%20be%20to%20their%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Tara%20Kartha%20is%20a%20former%20director%20of%20the%20National%20Security%20Council%20Secretariat)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744365660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fkqgmt7pg_rana_625x300_11_A