dent%20Donald%20Trump%20engaged%20in%20insider%20trading%20or%20market%20manipulation%20by%20encouraging%20people%20to%20buy%20stocks%20just%20before%20his%20dramatic%20reversal%20on%20global%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWho%20in%20the%20administration%20knew%20about%20Trump's%20latest%20tariff%20flip%20flop%20ahead%20of%20time%3F%20Did%20anyone%20buy%20or%20sell%20stocks%2C%20and%20profit%20at%20the%20public's%20expense%3F%26quot%3B%20California%20Democratic%20Senator%20Adam%20Schiff%20posted%20on%20X%20on%20Wednesday.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20writing%20to%20the%20White%20House%20--%20the%20public%20has%20a%20right%20to%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemocratic%20members%20of%20the%20House%20Financial%20Services%20Committee%20wrote%20on%20X%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20President%20of%20the%20United%20States%20is%20literally%20engaging%20in%20the%20world's%20biggest%20market%20manipulation%20scheme.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accusations%20came%20as%20Trump%20posted%20a%20few%20minutes%20after%20Wall%20Street%20opened%20that%20%26quot%3BIT'S%20TIME%20TO%20BUY%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20hours%20later%2C%20he%20announced%20a%2090-day%20suspension%20of%20additional%20tariffs%20against%20dozens%20of%20countries%2C%20with%20the%20exception%20of%20China%2C%20triggering%20a%20historic%20stock%20market%20rebound.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20several%20days%20of%20collapse%2C%20the%20Dow%20Jones%20index%20ended%20Wednesday%20up%207.87%20percent%2C%20its%20biggest%20gain%20since%202008%2C%20and%20the%20Nasdaq%20up%2012.16%20percent%2C%20the%20most%20since%202001.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20also%20signed%20his%20post%20on%20Truth%20Social%20with%20the%20letters%20%26quot%3BDJT%26quot%3B%20--%20both%20his%20initials%20and%20the%20stock%20market%20abbreviation%20for%20his%20media%20company%2C%20Trump%20Media%20%26amp%3B%20Technology%20Group.%20The%20company's%20shares%20closed%20the%20day%20up%2021.67%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E