india.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Fgaming%2Fmarvel-rivals-season-2-release-date-emma-frost-addition-and-more%2Farticleshow%2F120199165.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Tahawwur%20Rana%20Probe%2C%20An%20ISI%20Link%2C%20And%20Two%20Names%3A%20Major%20Iqbal%2C%20Sameer%20Ali%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20Tahawwur%20Hussain%20Rana%2C%20the%20Canadian-Pakistani%20businessman%20and%20key%20conspirator%20in%20the%202008%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks%2C%20sits%20in%20a%20high-security%20cell%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20fresh%20interrogations%20and%20years-old%20indictments%20are%20peeling%20back%20layers%20of%20one%20of%20the%20most%20high-profile%20cases%20in%20modern%20Indian%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERana's%20extradition%20from%20the%20US%2C%20after%20a%20prolonged%20legal%20battle%2C%20has%20once%20again%20put%20the%20spotlight%20on%20the%20alleged%20role%20of%20Pakistan's%20Inter-Services%20Intelligence%20(ISI)%20in%20orchestrating%20the%20three-day%20siege%20that%20left%20166%20dead%2C%20including%20six%20Americans%2C%20in%20Mumbai.%20Central%20to%20this%20plot%20are%20two%20figures%3A%20Major%20Iqbal%20and%20Major%20Sameer%20Ali%2C%20accused%20ISI%20operatives%20who%20have%20been%20on%20the%20most%20wanted%20list%20of%20the%20anti-terror%20body%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA).%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20NIA%20sources%2C%20Rana%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20grilled%20over%20Major%20Iqbal%20and%20Major%20Sameer%20Ali's%20alleged%20involvement%20and%20whether%20they%20coordinated%20with%20him%20in%20the%20days%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Handler%3A%20Major%20Iqbal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%202018%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20(PTI)%20report%2C%20Major%20Iqbal%20-identified%20in%20a%202010%20Chicago%20indictment%20as%20a%20serving%20ISI%20officer%20-%20was%20no%20peripheral%20player.%20He%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20being%20the%20person%20who%20financed%2C%20directed%2C%20and%20micromanaged%20the%20reconnaissance%20missions%20conducted%20by%20David%20Coleman%20Headley%2C%20the%20Pakistani-American%20double%20agent%20whose%20scouting%20of%20Mumbai's%20landmarks%20enabled%20the%20carnage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeadley%2C%20who%20pleaded%20guilty%20in%202010%20to%20avoid%20the%20death%20penalty%2C%20has%20described%20Major%20Iqbal%20as%20his%20primary%20ISI%20handler%2C%20part%20of%20a%20trio%20of%20agency%20officials%20who%20%26quot%3Brecruited%2C%20trained%2C%20and%20directed%26quot%3B%20him.%20In%20a%20testimony%20in%202011%2C%20Headley%20revealed%20over%2020%20email%20exchanges%20with%20an%20individual%20he%20knew%20as%20%26quot%3BChaudhery%20Khan%26quot%3B%20-%20an%20alias%20for%20Major%20Iqbal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20May%202008%20email%20discussed%20exploiting%20Rajaram%20Rege%2C%20then%20a%20Shiv%20Sena%20member%2C%20to%20bolster%20their%20cover.%20%26quot%3BHeadley%20had%20met%20me%20outside%20the%20Sena%20Bhavan%20with%20one%20Vilas%20Warke.%20He%20wanted%20me%20to%20show%20him%20the%20Sena%20Bhavan%20from%20inside%20but%20I%20had%20flatly%20declined%20his%20request.%20My%20meeting%20with%20him%20had%20only%20lasted%20two%20minutes%2C%26quot%3B%20Rajaram%20Rege%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20email%20instructed%20Headley%20to%20update%20Major%20Iqbal%20on%20%26quot%3Bthe%20projects%26quot%3B%20and%20surveillance%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20indictment%20described%20Major%20Iqbal%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20resident%20of%20Pakistan%20who%20participated%20in%20planning%20and%20funding%20attacks%20by%20Lashkar%26quot%3B%20and%20charged%20him%20with%20six%20counts%20of%20aiding%20terrorism%20and%20murder%2C%20alleging%20he%20funneled%20funds%20and%20resources%20to%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20(LeT)%2C%20the%20Pakistan-based%20terrorist%20group%20behind%20the%20attacks.%20Yet%2C%20conspicuously%20absent%20from%20the%20document%20is%20any%20explicit%20mention%20of%20the%20ISI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Control%20Room%3A%20Major%20Sameer%20Ali%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Major%20Iqbal%20was%20the%20architect%2C%20Major%20Sameer%20Ali%20-%20another%20accused%20ISI%20officer%20-%20was%20the%20field%20marshal.%20According%20to%2026%2F11%20handler%20Zabiuddin%20Ansari%20(alias%20Abu%20Jundal)%20who%20was%20arrested%20by%20Delhi%20Police%20in%202012%2C%20Sameer%20Ali%20oversaw%20the%20attacks%20in%20real-time%20from%20a%20LeT%20control%20room%20in%20Karachi's%20Malir%20Cantonment%2C%20a%20military%20garrison%20area.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJundal%2C%20in%20his%20testimony%2C%20described%20Sameer%20Ali%20issuing%20directives%20to%20LeT%20commander%20Zaki-ur-Rehman%20Lakhvi%20during%20the%20siege.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterpol's%20Red%20Notice%20for%20Sameer%20Ali%20describes%20him%20as%20born%20in%20Lahore%20in%201966%2C%20fluent%20in%20Urdu%2C%20Hindi%2C%20and%20English%2C%20and%20wanted%20by%20India%20for%20organised%20crime%20and%20terrorism.%20Yet%2C%20Pakistan%20has%20repeatedly%20denied%20his%20existence%2C%20dismissing%20him%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bfictitious%20character.%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%202012%20Economic%20Times%20report%2C%20Jundal%20told%20interrogators%20that%20Pakistan's%20own%20Federal%20Investigation%20Agency%20(FIA)%20raided%20and%20destroyed%20the%20Karachi%20control%20room%2C%20weeks%20after%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20attacks.%20Months%20later%2C%20they%20arrested%20Lakhvi%20at%20Baitul%20Mujahideen%20camp%20in%20Muzaffarabad%20in%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir%20-%20though%20Jundal%20and%20Abu%20Qahafa%20-%20a%20combat%20trainer%20named%20in%20the%20indictment%2C%20escaped%20through%20a%20rear%20exit.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744357380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fhuh74q1o_tahawwur-rana-_625x300_11_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%