20Mohammad%20Younis%20Malik%2C%20Vice%20Chairman%20of%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Lake%20Conservation%20and%20Management%20Authority%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20authority%E2%80%99s%20establishment%20in%201997%2C%20one%20of%20the%20major%20challenges%20we%20have%20faced%20has%20been%20the%20effective%20management%20and%20disposal%20of%20waste%2C%20including%20solid%2C%20liquid%2C%20and%20biomass%20from%20the%20lake%20and%20its%20surrounding%20areas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20accumulation%20of%20these%20waste%20materials%20has%20posed%20serious%20environmental%20threats.%20In%20response%20to%20this%2C%20we%20partnered%20with%20the%20CEF%20Group%20because%20they%20provided%20a%20tangible%20solution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202024%2C%20after%20years%20of%20research%2C%20trials%2C%20and%20construction%20of%20the%20plant%2C%20the%20project%20was%20virtually%20inaugurated%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Maninder%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20lake%20weeds%20to%20organic%20manure%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20of%20transforming%20lake%20weeds%20into%20valuable%20organic%20manure%20is%20unerring.%20Lake%20weeds%20collected%20by%20LCMA%E2%80%99s%20authorised%20vendors%20are%20transported%20to%20the%20processing%20plant%20using%204-5%20ton%20trucks.%20Approximately%2021%20trucks%20are%20deployed%20near%20the%20lake%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20task%20from%20April%20to%20December%2C%20before%20the%20lake%20starts%20freezing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20weeds%20are%20first%20weighed%20to%20maintain%20proper%20records%20before%20being%20unloaded%20in%20a%20designated%20area%20for%20processing%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20social%20entrepreneur%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weeds%20are%20first%20dried%20in%20a%20dewatering%20plant%20to%20remove%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288849%2Feasy-monsoon-hacks-to-protect-your-home-from-damp-smell-moisture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20much%20moisture%20as%20possible%3C%2Fa%3E.%20After%20that%2C%20they%20go%20through%20a%20two-step%20shredding%20process%20that%20breaks%20them%20down%20into%20small%20pieces%2C%20each%20less%20than%204%20mm%20in%20size.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20produce%20higher-quality%20manure%20when%20it%20is%20finely%20shredded%2C%E2%80%9D%20Maninder%20explains.%20The%20shredded%20material%20is%20then%20placed%20in%20windrows%20(3m%20wide%2C%2090m%20long)%20for%20controlled%20composting%20over%20two%20to%20three%20weeks.%20Afterward%2C%20it%20is%20sun-dried%20to%20further%20reduce%20moisture.%20Bio-nutrients%20and%20organic%20enhancers%20are%20added%20to%20improve%20the%20manure%E2%80%99s%20NPK%20(Nitrogen%2C%20Phosphorus%2C%20and%20Potassium)%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20composting%20process%2C%20the%20material%20is%20screened%2C%20refined%20into%20a%20powdered%20form%2C%20and%20packed%20in%20bags%20of%20various%20sizes%20for%20distribution.%20The%20entire%20process%20takes%20about%2035%E2%80%9340%20days%20from%20arrival%20to%20packaging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20people%20behind%20the%20progress%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20distribution%20network%20is%20one%20of%20the%20main%20reasons%20behind%20our%20success%2C%20and%20we%20are%20fortunate%20to%20have%20a%20group%20of%20over%20300%20dedicated%20and%20trusted%20partners%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20Leading%20the%20charge%20are%20five%20main%20distributors%20who%20manage%20regions%20across%20Kashmir%20with%20expertise%20and%20commitment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20include%20Sheezan%20Trading%20Co%2C%20headed%20by%20Jowhar%20Wani%2C%20which%20covers%20the%20entire%20valley%20from%20Nowgam%3B%20Alhuda%20Enterprises%2C%20led%20by%20Khalidul%20Islam%2C%20which%20plays%20a%20vital%20role%20in%20Shopian%3B%20and%20Lucky%20Enterprises%2C%20under