%20and%20scalability%2C%20which%20not%20only%20addresses%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F418606%2Fmanoj-mahajan-ias-initiative-for-waste-management-in-rural-sundargarh-odisha-empower-women%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewaste%20management%20issue%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Dal%20Lake%20but%20also%20offers%20a%20replicable%20model%20for%20other%20lake%20conservation%20projects.%20The%20initiative%20has%20had%20a%20positive%20environmental%20impact%20by%20converting%20lake%20biomass%20into%20bio-manure%2C%20contributing%20to%20both%20conservation%20efforts%20and%20agricultural%20sustainability%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGreener%20lakes%2C%20stronger%20communities%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20environmental%20impact%2C%20CEF%20Group%20has%20made%20strides%20in%20managing%20the%20excess%20lake%20weed.%20Between%20August%20and%20December%202024%2C%20they%20received%20a%20total%20of%2014%2C864%20tonnes%20of%20lake%20weed.%20Out%20of%20this%2C%204%2C131%20tonnes%20were%20converted%20into%20organic%20manure%2C%20a%20process%20that%20has%20led%20to%20a%20reduction%20of%20approximately%202%2C891%20tonnes%20of%20CO%E2%82%82%20emissions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20perspective%2C%20converting%20just%20one%20tonne%20of%20lake%20weed%20into%20organic%20manure%20results%20in%20a%20CO2%20savings%20of%20around%200.7%20tonnes.%20%E2%80%9COur%20project%20is%20designed%20to%20process%20up%20to%2070%2C000%20tonnes%20of%20lake%20weed%20each%20year%2C%20which%20yields%20between%2020%2C000%20to%2022%2C000%20tonnes%20of%20organic%20manure.%20This%20large-scale%20effort%20is%20expected%20to%20lead%20to%20an%20annual%20reduction%20of%20around%2050%2C000%20tonnes%20of%20CO%E2%82%82%20emissions%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Maninder%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20important%20aspect%20of%20this%20process%20is%20the%20leachate%20treatment%2C%20which%20involves%20the%20water%20that%20is%20extracted%20from%20the%20lake%20weeds.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20water%20that%20comes%20out%20of%20the%20lake%20weeds%20is%20carefully%20treated%20to%20remove%20any%20harmful%20contaminants%20like%20heavy%20metals%2C%20organic%20pollutants%2C%20and%20other%20toxic%20substances%2C%20through%20our%20leachate%20treatment%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20treated%2C%20this%20water%20is%20safely%20returned%20to%20the%20soil%2C%20ensuring%20that%20it%20nourishes%20the%20land%20without%20causing%20any%20negative%20environmental%20impact.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comprehensive%20approach%20not%20only%20helps%20manage%20the%20invasive%20lake%20weed%20problem%20but%20also%20contributes%20to%20sustainable%20agricultural%20practices%20by%20providing%20nutrient-rich%20organic%20manure%20while%20reducing%20carbon%20emissions%20and%20improving%20the%20health%20of%20the%20surrounding%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20the%20farmers%20of%20Kashmir%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20conversion%20has%20also%20benefitted%20around%202%2C500%20farmers%20in%20Kashmir%20so%20far%2C%20who%20now%20have%20access%20to%20organic%20manure%20at%20a%20lower%20price%20%E2%80%94%20Rs%2012%20per%20kg%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20Rs%2016%20per%20kg%20they%20were%20paying%20for%20chemical%20fertilisers%20brought%20in%20from%20other%20states%20like%20UP%20and%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20made%20an%20impact%20by%20enriching%20over%204%2C400%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20improving%20soil%20health%2C%20and%20supporting%20sustainable%20agriculture%20practices%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20the%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-26-at-12.15.55_f159d2ee-1-1744206017-500x750.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20organic%20manure%20has%20benefitted%20around%202%2C500%20farmers%20in%20Kashmir%20so%20far%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-26-at-12.15.55_f159d2ee-1-1744206017-500x750.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-26-at-12.15.55_f159d2ee-1-1744206017-200x300.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-26-at-12.15.55_f159d2ee-1-1744206017-768x1152.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-26-at-12.15.55_f159d2ee-1-1744206017-150x225.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-26-at-12.15.55_f159d2ee-1-1744206017.jpg%201000w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-418940%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20organic%20manure%20has%20benefitted%20around%202%2C500%20farmers%20in%20Kashmir%20so%20far%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESibir%20Hamdar%2C%20an%20apple%20farmer%20from%20the%20Shopian%20district%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20many%20years%2C%20I%20relied%20on%20chemical%20fertilisers%2C%20but%20their%20high%20cost%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F318062%2Fiit-bombay-scientist-dr-rajul-patkar-innovates-portable-soil-testing-device-for-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egradual%20degradation%20of%20soil%20quality%3C%2Fa%3E%20became%20a%20growing%20concern.%20As%20the%20expenses%20increased%2C%20it%20became%20difficult%20to%20maintain%20a%20good%20yield.%20However%2C%20since%20switching%20to%20organic%20manure%20provided%20by%20CEF%20Group%2C%20I%20have%20noticed%20a%20stark%20improvement%20in%20my%20orchard.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESibir%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20locally%20produced%20organic%20manure%20is%20not%20only%20more%20affordable%20but%20also%20rich%20in%20nutrients%20and%20completely%20natural.%20My%20apple%20trees%20are%20noticeably%20healthier%2C%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20fruit%20has%20improved%2C%20and%20the%20soil%20remains%20fertile%20without%20the%20need%20for%20harmful%20chemicals.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20the%20environment%20and%20farmers%20that%20have%20benefited.%20The%20project%20has%20created%20employment%20opportunities%20for%20the%20local%20community%2C%20with%2024%20people%20now%20working%20at%20the%20processing%20plant%20and%20hundreds%20of%20them%20helping%20collect%20weeds%20at%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohammed%20Adil%2C%20the%20site%20manager%20at%20CEF%20Group%20overseeing%20the%20scientific%20processing%20plant%20at%20CEF%20Srinagar%20Biofuel%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CCEF%20Group%E2%80%99s%20innovative%20waste%20processing%20plant%20has%20a%20capacity%20of%20140%20tonnes%20per%20day.%20By%20removing%20waste%20from%20Dal%20Lake%2C%20it%20directly%20improves%20water%20quality%2C%20restores%20biodiversity%2C%20and%20enhances%20the%20lake%E2%80%99s%20natural%20beauty.%20This%20has%20had%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20reviving%20tourism%20and%20boosting%20local%20businesses.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%20has%20also%20brought%20social%20benefits%2C%20creating%20over%201%2C500%20employment%20opportunities%2C%20particularly%20for%20local%20youth.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20these%20workers%20assist%20in%20collecting%20lake%20weeds%2C%20while%20others%20contribute%20directly%20to%20the%20operation%20of%20the%20plant%2C%E2%80%9D%20Adil%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98It%E2%80%99s%20a%20win-win%20for%20all%20of%20us%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20community%E2%80%99s%20response%20has%20been%20positive%2C%20even%20tho