ndia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-3_11zon-1744204780-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-3_11zon-1744204780-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-418882%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETransparency%20is%20key%20at%20CATCH%20Foundation%2C%20and%20the%20client%20is%20constantly%20kept%20in%20the%20know-how%20of%20the%20forest%E2%80%99s%20performance%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20selection%20of%20the%20site%2C%20too%2C%20is%20methodical%2C%20he%20adds.%20Every%20plot%20of%20land%20undergoes%20stringent%20assessment%20to%20ascertain%20its%20viability%20and%20the%20ecological%20implications%20of%20reforestation%20in%20the%20area.%C2%A0%20Take%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20the%20NSG%20campus.%20The%20campus%20is%20nestled%20in%20the%20Aravalli%20ranges%2C%20whose%20green%20undertones%20have%20been%20destroyed%20by%20rampant%20illegal%20mining%20and%20deforestation.%20The%20levels%20of%20destruction%20peaked%3B%20in%202009%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20banned%20illegal%20quarrying%20in%20the%20region.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Jagdish%20draws%20your%20attention%20to%20the%20other%2C%20lesser-known%20culprit%20that%20is%20also%20wreaking%20havoc%20in%20these%20hills.%20He%20shares%20how%20the%20invasive%20%3Cem%3Evilayati%20kikar%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Cem%3EProsopis%20juliflora%3C%2Fem%3E)%20was%20introduced%20into%20the%20region%20during%20colonial%20times%2C%20in%20a%20major%20upset%20to%20the%20land.%20It%20is%20out-competing%20the%20native%20flora%20of%20the%20hills.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%